item.title: C-Level! Cross Over a Spirit
item.content:encoded:
Mission C-Level! Cross Over a Spirit in which you can get Strawberry don't need Soul Candy. It is Rare but do not require Candy.

My first alt had Strawberry even before TicTac and Robogirl.

Please correct Wiki Page.
